title: California Takes A ZEV Sales Victory Lap Around Trump, And His Enablers
description:
California continues to celebrate strong ZEV sales despite the efforts of President Trump, and his Republican enablers in Congress, to throttle down the vehicle electrification movement.

The post California Takes A ZEV Sales Victory Lap Around Trump, And His Enablers appeared first on CleanTechnica.
